[Activate: Main] [Once Per Turn] If your Leader has the "Blackbeard Pirates" type, and this Character was played on this turn, K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a base cost of 3 or less.

OP10-OP10-087 normal.name: Tony Tony.Chopper (087)
OP10-OP10-087 normal.description: [Activate: Main] You may rest this Character and 1 of your "Dressrosa" type Leader or Stage cards: If your opponent has 5 or more cards in their hand, your opponent trashes 1 card from their hand. Then, trash 2 cards from the top of your deck.

[Blocker]

OP10-OP10-091 normal.name: Brook (091)

OP10-OP10-092 normal.name: Perona (092)
OP10-OP10-092 normal.description: [Activate: Main] [Once Per Turn] You may place 2 "Thriller Bark Pirates" type cards from your trash at the bottom of your deck in any order: Up to 1 of your Characters other than [Perona] gains +2000 power during this turn.

OP10-OP10-093 normal.name: Saint Homing
OP10-OP10-093 normal.description: [Activate: Main] You may trash this Character: Up to 1 of your black Characters gains +3 cost until the end of your opponent's next turn.

OP10-OP10-095 normal.name: Roronoa Zoro (095)
OP10-OP10-095 normal.description: [On Play] You may rest 1 of your "Dressrosa" type Leader or Stage cards: K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a cost of 4 or less. Then, trash 2 cards from the top of your deck.

OP10-OP10-096 normal.name: There's No Longer Any Need for the Seven Warlords of the Sea!!!
OP10-OP10-096 normal.description:
[Main] K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's "The Seven Warlords of the Sea" type Characters with a cost of 8 or less.
[Trigger] K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's "The Seven Warlords of the Sea" type Characters with a cost of 4 or less.

OP10-OP10-097 normal.name: Gum-Gum Rhino Schneider
OP10-OP10-097 normal.description:

[Trigger] Draw 2 cards and trash 1 card from your hand.

OP10-OP10-098 normal.name: Liberation
OP10-OP10-098 normal.description:
[Main] If the number of your Characters is at least 2 less than the number of your opponent's Characters, K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a base cost of 6 or less and up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a base cost of 4 or less.
[Trigger] Negate the effect of up to 1 of each of your opponent's Leader and Character cards during this turn.

OP10-OP10-099 normal.name: Eustass"Captain"Kid (099)

OP10-OP10-099 parallel.name: Eustass"Captain"Kid (099) (Parallel)

OP10-OP10-100 normal.name: Inazuma

OP10-OP10-102 normal.name: Emporio.Ivankov
OP10-OP10-102 normal.description: [Activate: Main] [Once Per Turn] Up to 3 of your "Revolutionary Army" type Characters gain +1000 power during this turn. Then, add 1 card from the top of your Life cards to your hand.

Once per turn, this Character cannot be K.O.'d by your opponent's effects.
